  <section class="app-c-header-notice" aria-label="notice" role="region">
    <div class="app-c-header-notice__header">
      <h2 class="app-c-header-notice__title">The UK has left the EU and the transition period after Brexit comes to an end this year.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="app-c-header-notice__content">
      <p class="app-c-header-notice__text govuk-body">This page tells you what you'll need to do from 1 January 2021. It will be updated if anything changes.</p>
        <div class="app-c-header-notice__links">
            <p class="govuk-body app-c-header-notice__link-intro">For current information, read: </p>
            <ul class="app-c-header-notice__list govuk-list">
                <li><a data-module="track-click" data-track-category="no_deal_notice" data-track-action="/government/publications/business-continuity-planning" data-track-label=" Business continuity planning" class="app-c-header-notice__link" href="/government/publications/business-continuity-planning"> Business continuity planning</a></li>
                <li><a data-module="track-click" data-track-category="no_deal_notice" data-track-action="/government/publications/eu-settlement-scheme-employer-toolkit" data-track-label="EU Settlement Scheme: employer toolkit " class="app-c-header-notice__link" href="/government/publications/eu-settlement-scheme-employer-toolkit">EU Settlement Scheme: employer toolkit </a></li>
                <li><a data-module="track-click" data-track-category="no_deal_notice" data-track-action="https://ec.europa.eu/health/funding/programme_en" data-track-label="EU Third Health Programme" class="app-c-header-notice__link" href="https://ec.europa.eu/health/funding/programme_en">EU Third Health Programme</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="app-c-header-notice__text govuk-body">You can also read about <a data-module="track-click" data-track-category="no_deal_notice" data-track-action="/transition" data-track-label="the transition period" class="govuk-link" href="/transition">the transition period</a>.</p>
